  "remarks": "\nIgor Burmistrov is the Chief of Staff and First Deputy Commander of the Internal Troops of the Ministry of Internal Affairs. In this position he bears responsibility for the inhumane and degrading treatment of detainees, amounting to serious human rights violations and the repression of civil society, including torture, carried out in the detention facilities following the elections of 9 August.",
